    Rename columns from API results to work with gnomeR functions

    rename_columns.Rd

    Rename columns from API results to work with gnomeR functions

    Usage

    rename_columns(df_to_check)

    Arguments

    df_to_check

    a data frame for which to check colums

    Value

    a renamed data frame

    Examples

    
rename_columns(df_to_check = oncokbR::blca_mutation)
